headline.main: Europe's Trend: Austria, Once Open, Now Shows Migrants Door
headline.print_headline: Europe's Trend: Austria, Once Open, Now Shows Migrants Door

lead_paragraph: Austria was among the first countries in Europe to put out the welcome mat when waves of people fleeing war and poverty reached the continent. Now, its focus is showing them the door.
